  # Get Weather Observations - All Airports
  
  Retrieve current weather observations from all available airports.
  
  ## Query Parameters
  - `limit`: Number of observations (default: 20, max: 100)
  - `airport`: Filter by specific airport code (optional)
  
  ## Weather Data Fields
  - `obs_id`: Unique observation identifier
  - `valid_time_gmt`: Observation time (Unix timestamp)
  - `wx_phrase`: Weather condition description
  - `temp`: Temperature (Â°F)
  - `precip_hrly`: Hourly precipitation (inches)
  - `snow_hrly`: Hourly snowfall (inches)
  - `wspd`: Wind speed (mph)
  - `clds`: Cloud coverage code (CLR, FEW, SCT, BKN, OVC)
  - `rh`: Relative humidity (%)
  - `vis`: Visibility (miles)
  
  ## Weather Phrases
  Clear conditions: Clear, Fair, Few Clouds, Partly Cloudy
  Cloudy conditions: Mostly Cloudy, Cloudy, Overcast, Scattered Clouds
  Rain: Light Rain, Rain, Heavy Rain, Drizzle, Showers
  Storms: Thunderstorms, Scattered Thunderstorms
  Winter: Light Snow, Snow, Heavy Snow, Freezing Rain, Sleet
  Reduced visibility: Fog, Haze, Mist
  Wind: Windy, Breezy
  
  ## Use Cases
  - Flight delay analysis by weather conditions
  - Airport operational impact assessment
  - Historical weather pattern analysis
  - Correlation with flight reliability metrics
}
